### User Stories\par
\par
This site is intended for readers and creators of new eNovels, eComics and other literary works in the growing foreign language publications market of east Asia. These publications re typically provided on a chapter by chapter basis offereing novel challenges in terms of dealing with management and presentation of products.\par
**_"As administrator I would like to"_**\par
* easily manage site to provide titles of interest in an attractive format\par
* attract new titles and provide a mechanism for translation of new works \par
 * generate ongoing interest in the site & build a reader/writer community\par
* make a profit from selling access to chapters and/or subscriptions to titles\par
* securely collect/make payments for works\par
\par
**_"As a reader I would like"_**\par
* view all products and blog posts without logging in \par
* view the site from any device (mobile, tablet, desktop)\par
* leave a review for products I liked\par
* be able to register and log in/out\par
* be able to change my password \par
* filter products based on type/genre/rating\par
* find products suiting my taste \par
* search through titles\par
* find products of a particular type e.g. sci-fi\par
* rate products I have read\par
* see newest titles\par
* have a bookbag I can easily add and remove titles/subscriptions from\par
* to be able to buy related titles\par
* be part of the community by creating or translating new works\par
* do all the above on an easily navigated and attractive website \par
